#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:2
msgid "策略快照、启动门禁与长期可观测（5-A / 5-B / 5-C）"
msgstr ""
"Policy snapshots, access control activation, and long-term observability "
"(5-A / 5-B / 5-C)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:4
msgid ""
"亲爱的用户，本章介绍三项**进阶**能力：策略运行前的**数据快照**、开盘前的"
"**启动门禁**、以及长跑时的**对账与日志**。若您尚未跑通基础 live，请先阅"
"读 :doc:`2-configuration-and-run`。"
msgstr ""
"Dear user, this chapter introduces three **advanced** capabilities: "
"**data snapshots** before strategy execution, **startup access control** "
"before market opening, and **reconciliation and logging** during long "
"runs. If you haven't yet successfully run the basic Live application, "
"please read :doc:`2-configuration-and-run` first."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:6
msgid ""
"> **本章解决什么问题** > 分钟级策略若在每一步都重复拉数据，既慢又容易缺行"
"情；开盘前若配置或数据未就绪就下单，风险大。我们把这些检查做成可配置机"
"制，并在日志里留痕，便于您复盘。"
msgstr ""
"**What problem does this chapter address?** Minute-level strategies that "
"repeatedly pull data at every step are slow and prone to missing market "
"data; placing orders before the market opens without proper "
"configuration or data carries significant risk. We've made these checks "
"configurable and logged them for easy review."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:10
msgid "内部代号对照（维护者/冒烟文档会用到）"
msgstr "Internal code name mapping (used by maintainers/smoke documents)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:12
msgid ""
"在 qteasy live 演进中，**5-A / 5-B / 5-C** 分别指策略快照、启动门禁与长期"
"可观测三类能力。冒烟文档与维护者笔记会使用代号；作为用户，您只需记住右侧"
"「用户向名称」即可。下表建立代号与日常说法的对应关系——阅读本章后文时，可"
"将「5-B」理解为「启动门禁」。"
msgstr ""
"In the evolution of qteasy live, **5-A / 5-B / 5-C** refer to three "
"capabilities: policy snapshots, activation access control, and long-term "
"observability, respectively. Smoke documentation and maintainer's notes "
"will use codenames; as a user, you only need to remember the \"user-"
"directed name\" on the right. The table below establishes the "
"correspondence between the codenames and common usage—when reading the "
"rest of this chapter, you can understand \"5-B\" as \"activation access "
"control.\""

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:14
msgid ""
"**各列含义**：**代号**为内部阶段编号；**用户向名称**为文档推荐叫法；**一"
"句话**为该能力在 live 链路中的位置。"
msgstr ""
"**Meaning of each column:** **Code** is the internal stage number; "
"**User-assigned name** is the recommended name in the documentation; "
"**One sentence** indicates the position of this capability in the live "
"pipeline."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:16
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：看到正文出现 ``5-A`` 等代号时查本表；配置键名称见 :doc:`2-"
"configuration-and-run` §4「策略快照」「启动门禁」行。"
msgstr ""
"**How to use:** When you see codes such as `5-A` in the main text, refer "
"to this table; see the configuration key name in :doc:`2-configuration-"
"and-run` §4 \"Policy Snapshot\" \"Start Access Control\" line."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:22
msgid "代号"
msgstr "code name"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:23
msgid "用户向名称"
msgstr "User name"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:24
msgid "一句话"
msgstr "In short"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:25
msgid "**5-A**"
msgstr "**5-A**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:26
msgid "策略快照"
msgstr "Strategy Snapshot"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:27
msgid "策略运行前预先拉好数据，本步复用，减少重复 IO"
msgstr ""
"Data is pre-fetched before the strategy runs, and this step reuses the "
"data to reduce redundant I/O."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:28
msgid "**5-B**"
msgstr "**5-B**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:29
msgid "启动门禁"
msgstr "Activate access control"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:30
msgid "开盘/run 前检查就绪状态，失败可告警或阻断"
msgstr ""
"Before opening/running, check the readiness status; if it fails, an "
"alarm or block should be triggered."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:31
msgid "**5-C**"
msgstr "**5-C**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:32
msgid "长期可观测"
msgstr "Long-term observable"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:33
msgid "订单与券商号映射、risk 日志轮换、对账与在途单诊断"
msgstr ""
"Order mapping with brokerage account, risk log rotation, reconciliation "
"and diagnosis of orders in transit"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:36
msgid "5-A：策略快照（prepare_strategy_snapshot）"
msgstr "5-A: Strategy Snapshot"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:38
msgid ""
"**您可以把它理解为**：每次策略要「上考场」前，先把试卷和材料在案头摆好；"
"真正答题时不再临时跑去打印室。"
msgstr ""
"You can think of it as follows: Before each \"exam,\" prepare the test "
"paper and materials on your desk; when you're actually answering the "
"questions, you no longer need to rush to the printing room."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:40
msgid ""
"当 ``live_trade_split_strategy_prepare=True`` 时，qteasy 会在每个 "
"``run_strategy`` 计划时刻**之前**插入 ``prepare_strategy_snapshot`` 任务"
"（提前量由 ``live_trade_prepare_lead_seconds`` 控制；``0`` 表示同刻入队，"
"但排序仍保证先 prepare）。"
msgstr ""
"When `live_trade_split_strategy_prepare=True`, qteasy will insert a "
"`prepare_strategy_snapshot` task **before** each `run_strategy` "
"scheduled time (the lead time is controlled by "
"`live_trade_prepare_lead_seconds`; `0` means enqueuing at the same time, "
"but the order still guarantees that prepare is first)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:41
msgid ""
"``prepare_strategy_snapshot`` 内完成原先 ``run_strategy`` 前的重活：子日"
"频数据刷新、准备数据缓冲、更新 live 价、注入过程数据等；完成后在内存留下"
"「快照有效」标记（交易日 + 步序号 + 时间）。"
msgstr ""
"The `prepare_strategy_snapshot` function completes the heavy lifting "
"that was done before `run_strategy`: refreshing sub-day frequency data, "
"preparing data buffers, updating live prices, and injecting process "
"data; after completion, it leaves a \"snapshot valid\" marker in memory "
"(trading day + step number + time)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:42
msgid ""
"随后 ``run_strategy`` 若发现快照仍在 "
"``live_trade_strategy_snapshot_max_age_seconds`` 内且步序号一致，则**不再"
"重复**上述拉取；否则记 ``snapshot_missing`` / ``snapshot_stale`` 并**跳过"
"本步策略**（避免用过期数据算信号）。"
msgstr ""
"Subsequently, if `run_strategy` finds that the snapshot is still within "
"`live_trade_strategy_snapshot_max_age_seconds` and the step number is "
"consistent, then **the above fetching will not be repeated**; otherwise, "
"`snapshot_missing` / `snapshot_stale` is recorded and this step's "
"strategy is **skipped** (to avoid using expired data to calculate "
"signals)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:43
msgid ""
"开启 split 时，``prepare_strategy_snapshot`` 与 ``run_strategy`` 在**主线"
"程同步**执行（与异步拉 live 价的任务分离），避免多线程同时碰 Operator。"
msgstr ""
"When split is enabled, `prepare_strategy_snapshot` and `run_strategy` "
"are executed synchronously on the main thread (separated from "
"asynchronous live pricing tasks), avoiding multiple threads from "
"simultaneously accessing the Operator."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:45
msgid ""
"**与真实行为的差异**：快照在内存中，进程重启后需重新 prepare；不是磁盘上"
"的永久缓存。"
msgstr ""
"**Differences from actual behavior**: Snapshots are in memory and need "
"to be prepared again after the process restarts; they are not permanent "
"caches on disk."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:48
msgid "5-B：启动门禁（run_startup_gate）"
msgstr "5-B: Start the access control (run_startup_gate)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:50
msgid ""
"**您可以把它理解为**：发车前的**安全检查**——策略是否就绪、必要数据表是否"
"在、（可选）本地账本是否与券商端一致。"
msgstr ""
"You can think of it as: a safety check before departure – whether the "
"strategy is ready, whether the necessary data tables are available, and "
"(optionally) whether the local ledger is consistent with the brokerage's "
"end."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:52
msgid "``live_trade_startup_gate_mode``："
msgstr "``live_trade_startup_gate_mode``:"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:54
msgid "``off`` — 关闭门禁"
msgstr "`off` — Turn off access control"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:55
msgid "``warn`` — 失败只记日志/trace，**仍允许**交易（建议灰度先用）"
msgstr ""
"`warn` — Failures are only logged/traced, **but transactions are still "
"allowed** (recommended for gradual rollout first)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:56
msgid ""
"``block`` — 失败则拒绝 ``run_strategy`` 入队"
"（``skip_reason=gate_failed``）"
msgstr ""
"`block` — rejects if it fails. `run_strategy` is then queued "
"(`skip_reason=gate_failed`)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:58
msgid "Trader 在生成当日日程后会调用门禁（非交易日快速跳过）。"
msgstr ""
"Trader will invoke the access control after generating the daily "
"schedule (non-trading days are quickly skipped)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:59
msgid "检查分层（失败码会写入 trace ``failures``）："
msgstr ""
"Check the layering (failure codes will be written to the trace "
"``failures`):"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:61
msgid "**L1**：Operator 是否就绪、账户是否存在"
msgstr "**L1:** Is the Operator ready? Does the account exist?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:62
msgid "**L2**：主历史表是否在数据源中（按 ``asset_type`` 映射日频表等）"
msgstr ""
"**L2:** Whether the main history table is in the data source (mapped to "
"daily frequency table by `asset_type`, etc.)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:63
msgid ""
"**L3**（可选）：若 Broker 返回非空远端现金/持仓，则与本地比对；未实现远"
"端 API 时不硬比"
msgstr ""
"**L3** (Optional): If the Broker returns a non-empty remote cash/"
"position, compare it with the local one; do not perform a hard "
"comparison if the remote API is not implemented."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:65
msgid "手工冒烟全清单见 :doc:`7-manual-smoke-live-grid-roadmap`。"
msgstr ""
"For a complete list of manual smoke-live grid roads, see :doc:`7-manual-"
"smoke-live-grid-roadmap`."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:68
msgid "5-C：账本、日志与恢复可观测"
msgstr "5-C: Ledger, Logs, and Recovery Observability"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:70
msgid ""
"在 5-A/5-B 之上，便于**长跑排障与审计**（**不含**自动改单/补偿；真实 QMT "
"远端查询属后续版本）："
msgstr ""
"Above 5-A/5-B, it facilitates **long-distance troubleshooting and "
"auditing** (**excluding** automatic order modification/compensation; "
"actual QMT remote querying is a later version):"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:72
msgid ""
"**订单 ↔ 券商号映射**：受理成功后回写 ``broker_order_id`` / "
"``broker_name``；受理拒单则 ``rejected`` 且 broker 字段空。"
msgstr ""
"**Order ↔ Broker ID Mapping**: Upon successful acceptance, "
"``broker_order_id`` / ``broker_name`` will be written back; if the order "
"is rejected, ``rejected`` will be written back and the broker field will "
"be empty."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:73
msgid ""
"**日志轮换扩展**：``rotate_trade_logs`` 除 trade CSV 外也清理超期 "
"``*.risk.log``（规则见 :doc:`5-artifacts-and-troubleshooting`）。"
msgstr ""
"**Log Rotation Extension**: `rotate_trade_logs` cleans up expired "
"`*.risk.log` in addition to trade CSV (see :doc:`5-artifacts-and-"
"troubleshooting` for rules)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:74
msgid "**对账与诊断 trace**："
msgstr "**Reconciliation and Diagnosis Trace:**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:76
msgid ""
"``pre_open`` / ``post_close`` 后输出 ``reconcile`` 检查点"
"（``checkpoint_passed`` / ``checkpoint_warn`` 等）"
msgstr ""
"The `pre_open` and `post_close` commands output the `reconcile` "
"checkpoint (e.g., `checkpoint_passed`, `checkpoint_warn`)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:77
msgid ""
"DEBUG 任务 ``diagnose_pending_orders``：只读对比本地与远端在途单差异"
msgstr ""
"DEBUG task ``diagnose_pending_orders`: Read-only comparison of local and "
"remote pending orders."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:80
msgid "给新手的结论：两种「拒单」"
msgstr "Conclusion for beginners: Two types of \"order rejection\""

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:82
msgid ""
"在 live 订单链路中，「被拒」可能发生在 **RiskManager 复核台**（风控）或 "
"**Broker 受理**（柜台）两个站点，证据位置完全不同。:doc:`3-risk-and-"
"order-lifecycle` 已从流程角度说明；下表从**订单表与 broker_order_id** 角"
"度给出对照，供排错时快速对号入座。"
msgstr ""
"In the live order process, \"rejection\" can occur at either the "
"**RiskManager review desk** (risk control) or the **Broker processing** "
"(counter), where the evidence is located in completely different places. "
"The `3-risk-and-order-lifecycle` documentation has already explained "
"this from a process perspective; the table below provides a comparison "
"between the **order table** and the **broker_order_id** for quick "
"troubleshooting."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:84
msgid ""
"**各列含义**：**路径**为拒单/成功类型；**本地订单表**是否新增行；"
"**broker_order_id** 是否回写；**审计**建议优先打开的文件或表。"
msgstr ""
"**Column Meanings:** **Path** indicates order rejection/success type; "
"**Local Order Table** indicates whether a new row has been added; "
"**broker_order_id** indicates whether a write-back is required; "
"**Audit** indicates the file or table that is recommended to be opened "
"first."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:86
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：CLI 有 risk 英文拒因且无新订单 → 第一行；订单列表出现 "
"``rejected`` 且 broker 号空 → 第二行；有 broker 号 → 第三行，再查成交状"
"态。"
msgstr ""
"**How to use:** CLI shows a risky rejection reason and no new orders → "
"first line; order list shows \"rejected\" and broker number is empty → "
"second line; broker number exists → third line, then check the "
"transaction status."

#: ../../source/live_trading/6-trader-snapshot-gate.rst:88
msgid ""
"**示例**：``risk_log`` 含 ``<RISK REJECTED>`` 且 ``orders`` 无对应新单 → "
"风控拒单，勿去查券商 connect。"
msgstr ""
"**Example:** `risk_log` contains ``<RISK REJECTED> Furthermore, if there "
"are no corresponding new orders in the \"orders\" section, the order "
"will be rejected by risk control. Do not check the brokerage's "
"connection information."

